<title>ITALY: Italy Saipem proposes 140 lire dividend.</title>
<headline>Italy Saipem proposes 140 lire dividend.</headline>
<dateline>ROME 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Italian oil engineering company Saipem SpA said on Tuesday that it would propose a 1996 dividend of 140 lire per ordinary share and 170 lire per savings share compared with 120 and 150 respectively for 1995.</p>
<p>A company statement said the board proposal would be put to a shareholders' meeting for approval on April 30. The dividends are payable from May 19, the statement said.</p>
<p>--Rome newsroom +39 6 678 2505</p>
